which is called map.

00:00:28.920 --> 00:00:32.220
First, I want to quickly show you something which will help you

00:00:32.220 --> 00:00:35.595
see the difference between map and forEach.

00:00:35.595 --> 00:00:42.385
If we go ahead and remove the upperCaseName array and place,

